{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d843f8a055","title":"右派言论——反对农业合作化","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f37a6553af","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"d843f8a055"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"4e42fca317","name":"张存根"},{"id":"5a2bbcc647","name":"北京钢铁学院"},{"id":"63d036a92b","name":"张振华"},{"id":"bd40a5fcaf","name":"张庆瑶"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4e01c59911","type":"title","text":"右派言论——反对农业合作化","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055"},{"id":"49cadcdf0c","type":"authors","text":"北京钢铁学院张存根张庆瑶张振华","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055"},{"id":"14ddec6234","type":"paragraph","text":"“农业合作化是搞糟了的，农民为了工分，失去了竞争性，现在乡下是乱极了，乡下生活水平太低了。”（北京钢铁学院　张存根）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055"},{"id":"add4959090","type":"paragraph","text":"“合作化是由毛主席一篇报告搞起来的，是否有点主观？","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055"},{"id":"eec0afad45","type":"paragraph","text":"农业合作化不如不合作化。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055"},{"id":"f120650bcf","type":"paragraph","text":"对生产来说（据合作社）这是损失，一切靠社听上级安排人们的主动性就太少了，好多人不往前干了，不望发财了，只等着跟着别人到社会主义。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055"},{"id":"458ec466c3","type":"paragraph","text":"合作化的缺点：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055"},{"id":"fbfec62e05","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）办社农民脱离劳动机构大，人们的主动性少了，处处听指示，在一旁静候。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055"},{"id":"666754c34c","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）入社前干活有劲，有计划的人现在没有用处了，入社后，活儿轻收入减少了。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055"},{"id":"2ddcde1cd5","type":"subtitle","text":"（3）好多人劳动积极性对生产的主动性降低得很厉害。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055"},{"id":"887c1face0","type":"paragraph","text":"在工作过程中工作方法上相当普遍地发生过严重的错误，相当普遍地采取了侵犯农民威严的办法，几乎有对地主办法的色彩，有的地方逼粮有没有饿死人命？","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055"},{"id":"add6881991","type":"paragraph","text":"要不是后来改过来，要不是共产党为人民作了那么多好事，以致冲淡了这些错误，人民会大为不满的，这是党的威信惯性起作用。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055"},{"id":"ff3b65cb62","type":"paragraph","text":"葛佩琦言论中说，统购统销搞错了，是有其片面的客观的观感看问题，片面是思想方法问题，不一定是什么背景不可。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055"},{"id":"c4f099465e","type":"paragraph","text":"对资产阶级满面春风，对富农就大大不同。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055"},{"id":"303d1e2546","type":"paragraph","text":"富农家是劳动起家，党对我家评成份不对”（原编者注：他家评为富农，他认为应是中农）。（北京钢铁学院  张庆瑶）","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055"},{"id":"27d100664d","type":"paragraph","text":"“合作化搞糟了，群众对干部不满，生产搞不好，粮食产量下降。合作化搞的太快，干部质量太差，作风太坏。”（北京钢铁学院  张振华）","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055"},{"id":"4980b2d25d","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055"}],"page":{"id":"9747f347f3","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d843f8a055","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}